data.eml:eml: Asiagomphus reinhardti sp. nov. (Odonata, Gomphidae) from eastern Cambodia and southern Laos

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Kosterin, Oleg E., Yokoi, Naoto (2016): Asiagomphus reinhardti sp. nov. (Odonata, Gomphidae) from eastern Cambodia and southern Laos. Zootaxa 4103 (1): 35-42, DOI: http://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4103.1.3
